笑话，而且他们找我就是带着目的和功利来的，一旦我没有给他们提供资源（比如考研真题网课种种帮助）他们就会远离我。我一直觉得人性不可考验，人为了自己的利益什么都做的出来，而且我认为人自身所有烦恼都来自人际关系，我不喜欢被这些杂事打扰，所以社交面也不广。但是我这样真实不做作的性格，好像融不进去一个圈子，也不屑于主动维持虚假功利的人际关系，不想变成一个圆滑世故的人，说话真实直爽，但为什么只要我不主动就没有人主动找我，而且有那么一两个主动找我的人，我也觉得他们是有利可图，不是真心朋友，随时会吃掉你"},"attached_info":"Cj8IkaeL7ZCbk7EuEAMaCDcyOTkwNDk1IJ6ls4wGMCw4hR5ALXIJNDk4MTkxMzY5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-9b43cdc540c19efb7de87a709b7a6cf0_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"46_1659694407.490286","card_id":"Q_546951069","target":{"id":546951069,"title":"米哈游新作《绝区零》于 8 月 5 日开启「调律测试」，你的体验如何？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/546951069","type":"question","created":1659601038,"answer_count":229,"follower_count":424,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[253,1750,166361,436225,2003653],"comment_count":12,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8IkaeL7ZCbk7EuEAMaCDgzODI3OTIyII6BrpcGMAw4qANALnIJNTQ2OTUxMDY5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"48 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-806e52e0ea40378b7091b81bcc67c31c_r.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"47_1659694407.4909174","card_id":"Q_46464362","target":{"id":46464362,"title":"该不该让小孩子在幼儿园学小学的知识？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/46464362","type":"question","created":1463541888,"answer_count":37,"follower_count":165,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2146,2724,3773],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"我妹妹马上上幼儿园大班、家里很纠结要不要让她转学到另一个幼儿园、因为现在这个幼儿园不教东西、家长怕上小学跟不上、该不该转到学小学知识的幼儿园？ 另：家长想让她上我们这边好一点的小学"},"attached_info":"Cj4IkaeL7Z